The evidence with the title 'Has Donald Trump overseen a gain of 500,000 jobs so far? | PolitiFact ' says Apr 26, 2017  ... On april 25, the White House launched a web page to promote president Donald Trump's achievements in his first 100 days. Featured prominently near the top was a graphic that touted job gains on Trump's watch. The graphic said, "over 500000 new jobs -- with a surge in female employment last month. 
